OL,3,C#2m support fund launched as
OL,4,Cpensioners prepare for rising energy
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,8,FScott looks at fears over the winter
OL,9,Ffuel allowance cuts and what's being
OL,10,Fdone to help pensioners.
OL,12,FEven before the Chancellor Rachel
OL,13,FReeves announces anticipated cuts and
OL,14,Ftax rises in the Budget, she's faced
OL,15,Fopposition from pensioners after
OL,16,Ftaking away the winter fuel allowance
OL,17,Ffrom many.
