OL,3,C#2m support fund launched as
OL,4,Cpensioners prepare for rising energy
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FPreviously, anyone over state pension
OL,8,Fage could receive the payment, but
OL,9,Fthis was changed by the new Labour
OL,10,FGovernment, meaning about 10 million
OL,11,Fpensioners will miss out this year.
OL,13,FGas supplier Cadent has put aside two
OL,14,Fmillion pounds to help pensioners save
OL,15,Ffuel and stay warm with measures like
OL,16,Ffree insulation and even supplying air
OL,17,Ffryers which provide cheaper ways of
OL,18,Fcooking.
