OL,7,FIn Blackpool, former nurse Jennifer
OL,8,FMunday is one of those being helped by
OL,9,Fthe scheme, but she's still dreading
OL,10,Flosing the #300 allowance that helped
OL,11,Fpay her fuel bills.
OL,13,FThe environmental charity organisation
OL,14,FGroundwork, have partnered with the
OL,15,FCadent Foundation to deliver some of
OL,16,Fthe measures it's hoped will help
OL,17,Fpensioners save fuel and money.
OL,19,FNeil Rimmer is a Green Doctor he says
OL,20,Fthe help they can give is 'life
OL,21,Fchanging'.
