OL,7,F"People don't always know what their
OL,8,Foptions are. So when we can go in and
OL,9,Fsay this is what we can do, we can get
OL,10,Fyour house sorted, get it insulated...
OL,11,Fthe first question is always how much
OL,12,Fwill this cost us? But obviously
OL,13,Fbecause of the Cadent Foundation we're
OL,14,Fable to supply these things, it is
OL,15,Flife changing."
OL,17,FHouseholds across Britain are facing
OL,18,Fincreasing energy costs this winter
OL,19,Fafter the regulator raised its price
OL,20,Fcap from October.
