OL,3,C#2m support fund launched as
OL,4,Cpensioners prepare for rising energy
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FAround 1.4 million pensioners are
OL,8,Falready receiving pension credit, but
OL,9,Fthe Government estimates up to 880,000
OL,10,Ffurther households are eligible for
OL,11,Fthe support for those with a low
OL,12,Fincome.
OL,14,FPeople receiving pension credit
OL,15,Fqualify for the winter fuel payment
OL,16,Fworth up to #300, to help with bills.
OL,18,FPeople are encouraged to contact their
OL,19,Fenergy supplier if they are worried
OL,20,Fabout paying their bills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
